<span id="freeTextContainer11101020366624769617">Hmmm. Uneven. Loved Patrice, her mother, Wood Mountain. It was two novels in one and I am not sure they came together well. A strange device of formatting it kind of like a play in certain chapters that was jarring. Erdrich is brilliant, though. I would read anything she wrote and enjoy the privilege. </span>

          </span>
